# Portfolio Project Rules

The canonical rulebook for this repo lives in `AGENTS.md` at the project root - project overview,
stack, brand and tone, design rules and references, architecture (folder structure, Server vs Client
Components, import alias, strict TypeScript), writing style, code style, git conventions, and
collaboration/explanation requirements.

Cursor reads `AGENTS.md` natively, so follow it as the source of truth. Edit shared rules there, not
here. This file exists only to keep those rules `alwaysApply` for the globs above.
